{
  "page": "Sable",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Thorensmallwoodmanzanedo.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c2/Thorensmallwoodmanzanedo.jpg/350px-Thorensmallwoodmanzanedo.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c2/Thorensmallwoodmanzanedo.jpg/525px-Thorensmallwoodmanzanedo.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c2/Thorensmallwoodmanzanedo.jpg/700px-Thorensmallwoodmanzanedo.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Thorensmallwoodmanzanedo.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Thoren_Smallwood\" title=\"Thoren Smallwood\">Thoren Smallwood</a> wearing the sable cloak of <a href=\"/index.php/Jaremy_Rykker\" title=\"Jaremy Rykker\">Jaremy Rykker</a>, by Antonio José Manzanedo © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p><b>Sables</b> are a species of marten similar to the <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/sable\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:sable\">real-life animal</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Culture\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Culture</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Culture\">Culture</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sable&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Culture\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Sables are hunted for their fur. Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Waymar_Royce\" title=\"Waymar Royce\">Waymar Royce</a> has a long sable cloak,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragotprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragotprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaremy_Rykker\" title=\"Jaremy Rykker\">Jaremy Rykker</a> has a heavy cloak richly trimmed with sable.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Ramsay_Snow\" title=\"Ramsay Snow\">Ramsay Snow</a> also has a sable cloak.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Wisdom <a href=\"/index.php/Hallyne\" title=\"Hallyne\">Hallyne</a> has striped black-and-scarlet robes trimmed with sable.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Arnolf_Karstark\" title=\"Arnolf Karstark\">Arnolf Karstark</a>'s grey wool cloak is trimmed with black sable.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> Sable trims the collar of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Denys_Mallister\" title=\"Denys Mallister\">Denys Mallister</a> and accents the sleeves of his black velvet doublet.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos78.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos78.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Sable_Hall\" title=\"Sable Hall\">Sable Hall</a> is one of the abandoned castles of the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a> along the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sable&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>While drinking <a href=\"/index.php/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">wine</a> in the barracks of <a href=\"/index.php/Castle_Black\" title=\"Castle Black\">Castle Black</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Gared\" title=\"Gared\">Gared</a> joked that Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Waymar_Royce\" title=\"Waymar Royce\">Waymar Royce</a> personally killed the sables for his fine cloak.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragotprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragotprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sable&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sable&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Royce_vs_other.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/ca/Royce_vs_other.jpg/350px-Royce_vs_other.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"197\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/ca/Royce_vs_other.jpg/525px-Royce_vs_other.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/ca/Royce_vs_other.jpg/700px-Royce_vs_other.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Royce_vs_other.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Waymar_Royce\" title=\"Waymar Royce\">Waymar Royce</a> facing <a href=\"/index.php/Others\" title=\"Others\">Others</a> while wearing a sable cloak, by Jon Neimeister © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Waymar_Royce\" title=\"Waymar Royce\">Waymar Royce</a>'s splendid sable cloak is slashed when the young <a href=\"/index.php/Ranger\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ranger\">ranger</a> is attacked by <a href=\"/index.php/Others\" title=\"Others\">Others</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Haunted_forest\" title=\"Haunted forest\">haunted forest</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragotprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragotprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sable&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Thoren_Smallwood\" title=\"Thoren Smallwood\">Thoren Smallwood</a> claims Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Jaremy_Rykker\" title=\"Jaremy Rykker\">Jaremy Rykker</a>'s sable cloak after his death.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok13.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Mace_Tyrell\" title=\"Mace Tyrell\">Mace Tyrell</a> and two of his sons, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Garlan_Tyrell\" title=\"Garlan Tyrell\">Garlan</a> and Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Loras_Tyrell\" title=\"Loras Tyrell\">Loras</a>, wear green velvet trimmed with sable while in the <a href=\"/index.php/Throne_room\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Throne room\">throne room</a> after the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Blackwater\" title=\"Battle of the Blackwater\">Battle of the Blackwater</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok65.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sable&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>King <a href=\"/index.php/Tommen_Baratheon\" title=\"Tommen Baratheon\">Tommen I Baratheon</a> wears cloth-of-gold beneath a sable mantle while attending the funeral of his grandfather, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc7.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Euron_Greyjoy\" title=\"Euron Greyjoy\">Euron Greyjoy</a> claims a sable cloak from Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Baelor_Blacktyde\" title=\"Baelor Blacktyde\">Baelor Blacktyde</a> after having him executed.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc29.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sable&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Frey\" title=\"Walda Frey\">Walda Bolton</a> wears a sable hood when Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Roose Bolton</a> returns to the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">north</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup> and Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Barbrey_Dustin\" title=\"Barbrey Dustin\">Barbrey Dustin</a> wraps herself in sable at <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd41.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sable&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><a href=\"/index.php/Waymar_Royce\" title=\"Waymar Royce\">His</a> cloak was his crowning glory; sable, thick and black and soft as sin.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragotprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragotprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Will\" title=\"Will\">Will</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Bet <a href=\"/index.php/Waymar_Royce\" title=\"Waymar Royce\">he</a> killed them all himself, he did, twisted their little heads off, our mighty warrior.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragotprologue.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a h